61B45D3D48BA63DE75B0B5A3EE573FD5: Apply an echo effect to input from a Patchwork audio generator before sending it to an output such as the Patchwork Speaker.
8AA60CAB4DE8E925AFC76E927B197D34: Apply an echo effect to input from a Patchwork audio generator before sending it to an output such as the Patchwork Speaker.

UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.Feedback.Desc: Controls the number of repetitions produced. Higher values will increase the intensity and length of the echo effect.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.Mix.Descripti: Determines how much of the audio output is processed by the effect.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.AllowPortSele: Determines if the Patchwork Tool can access any cable input or output ports on the device.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.EnabledOnPhas: Determines the game phases during which the device will be enabled. Pre-game includes all phases prior to start of game (like the pre-game lobby or countdown to start of game.) This setting does not affect Edit Mode.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.Disable.Descr: Disables the device when an event occurs.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.Enable.Descri: Enables the device when an event occurs.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.Filter.Descri: Filters the frequency of the delayed signal with a low-pass filter on the left and a high-pass filter on the right.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.LegalInfo.Des: Please note: Use of a Patchwork audio device is limited to the creation of new and original musical works.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.Style.Descrip: Selects the style for the chosen Sync Timing. "Straight" will output at the set Sync Timing, "Triplet" will output in a shuffle feel at two thirds of the Sync Timing, and "Dotted" will output in a syncopated feel at one and a half times the Sync Timing.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.AudioOut.Desc: Sets the destination for this device's Audio Out cable.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.AudioIn.Descr: Sets the inputs for this device's Audio In port.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.BeatIn.Descri: Sets the inputs for this device's Beat Delay knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.FeedbackIn.De: Sets the inputs for this device's Feedback knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.FilterIn.Desc: Sets the inputs for this device's Filter knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.MixIn.Descrip: Sets the inputs for this device's Mix knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.StyleIn.Descr: Sets the inputs for this device's Style carousel.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.BeatDelay.Des: Sets the time in musical increments that an echo is heard after the original source is played.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.OnDisabled.De: Triggers an event when the device is disabled.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularEchoEffect_C.OnEnabled.Des: Triggers an event when the device is enabled.
